        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>You use the power of nightmares to magically replicate the venomous attack of the aberrant and cunning Leng spiders. You deal [[/r 2d6 #piercing]] piercing damage to the touched creature and afflict it with Leng spider venom. If the target takes piercing damage, they must attempt a Fortitude save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target takes [[/r 2d6 #poison]] poison damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target is afflicted with Leng Spider Venom at stage 1.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is afflicted with Leng spider venom at stage 2.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Leng Spider Venom</strong> (incapacitation, poison) <strong>Level 13</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Maximum Duration</strong> 6 rounds</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> [[/r 2d6 #poison]] poison damage and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 1} (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> [[/r 3d6 #poison]] poison damage and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 2} (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> [[/r 4d6 #poison]] poison damage, @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 2}, and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Confused]{Confused} (1 round)</p>"
